_header: My little fool / Is gone to play
_description: His coy mistress — one short stanza with a ‘How frisca loly’ refrain

BLRoyApp58.Transcription:
My lytell foleYs gon to playsche wyll tary no longer with
                    mehe how frisca Iolyvnder the gryne wood trehe how fisca
                    Iolyvnder þe grene wood trehe how frisca Ioly
BLRoyApp58.Editions:
Flügel,  Ewald.

                VIII.”
